          <p>When you list only on Airbnb, you're effectively invisible to the audiences on every other platform. These aren't the same travelers searching in two places simultaneously. A family from Germany planning a Toronto trip is almost certainly searching Booking.com first, not Airbnb. A family of five from the US looking for a vacation home is probably on VRBO. You're not in front of them at all.</p>

